----------------
  nsfw-service
----------------

[ Usage ]

Send an HTTP POST request to port 9000 with the request body containing raw image data.

Supported formats: WEBP, PNG, GIF, JPEG.

Animated images are not supported. For GIFs, only the first frame is used.

--- Response Status Codes ---

200 – Image classified, response body is JSON
400 – Invalid image data
405 – Method not allowed (use POST)
411 – Failed to read request body
413 – Request body too large (max 16 MB)
415 – Unsupported image type
422 – Invalid image dimensions (>2048px or <32px)
500 – Server error, response body is plaintext

--- Example Response Body ---

{
   "allowed":true,
   "image":{
      "height":400,
      "width":400
   },
   "logits":{
      "drawing":0.6907269,
      "hentai":0.226651,
      "neutral":0.08234569,
      "porn":0.0002462058,
      "sexy":0.000030217838
   },
   "timings":{
      "classify":16636400,
      "decode":4752600,
      "probe": 7965500,
      "total": 29354500
   }
}

[ Hosting ]

This service is intended to run in a Docker container on Debian 13.

A public instance is available at: https://nsfw.panca.kz

Please do not abuse it. Uptime is best-effort only. If this service is mission
critical, you should host your own instance.

